I wont be able to post for about two weeks. I am going to my Aunts and they 
don't have internet. i'll try to, but i doubt it. Sorry. you can go on with 
out me though. I'll catch up!





* Snow Tech looks at the bolt of electricity fired at him. He knew it would 
be too late to get away, so he just stared at it with wide eye's. And, 
before it hit him, he said the one thing he could think of.*

" Oh S@#$!!"

* The lightning shot through him, making his fur seemingly explode off his 
body. The fur that was left on him, curled really tightly to his body, 
making him look like a french-poodle. He bounced around and stuttering.*

" d-dd-d-dd-dd-d-ddd-d!"

*He jittered into the bush again, falling on his ass. It would be up to 
Shadow Cat now.*

* Shadow Cat was flying high above the battle, oblivious to every thing till 
two missles flew past her and exploded. She growled. This was getting 
annoying. She lifted her arms to the sky and called with all her might for 
the great forces of the air, her eyes turning a bright purple. the wind 
began to pick-up around her and the clouds darkened. Electricity crackled 
and roared towards her at her call. It condensed around her body, hugging 
her like a lover might, until she was the lightning herself. She shaped 
herself into a torpedo shape and shot down towards the pred. No way was she 
going to miss this time!*
